<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        <p>Thank you for creating an account with us. Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        <p>This link will expire in 24 hours. If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 